<varlistentry id="options.AnimateTwist">
	<term>AnimateTwist <emphasis remap='I'>revolutions</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Tells Animate how many revolutions to twist the iconification frame.</para>
		<para>Note: The above configuration option "AnimateTwist" should not be confused with the AnimateResize mode "Twist".</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
